edu.stanford.smi.protegex.owl.swrl.portability
Interface OWLOntology

All Known Implementing Classes:
P3OWLOntology
public interface OWLOntology

Interface that is very roughly equivalent to the OWLAPI interfaces OWLOntology and OWLOntologyManager. All SWRLTab code in Protege-OWL will eventually use this interface to interact with an OWL ontology, thus easing the port to the OWLAPI. At present, this interface is not fully aligned with the OWLAPI.
